                       <para style="CENTRO7">Date: ___/___/______ </para></td>
                  <td> <para style="CENTRO7">Company approval: ([[ o.company_id.partner_id.name ]])</para>
                       <para style="CENTRO"> <font color="white"> </font> </para>
